          href="https://go.dev/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener">Golang</a
        > and <a href="https://www.php.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          >PHP</a
        > with <a href="https://symfony.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
          >Symfony framework</a
        >. I have also some professional working experience with <a
