        class="mb-8 mt-8 mx-auto"
        alt="My Hobbies"
        title="My Hobbies"
      />
      <p>
        Besides Programming, I like to hangout with friends, watch and play
        sports, TV Shows, and do activities outside like walking.
      </p>
